OL,3,CThames Water reports 40% rise in
OL,4,Cpollution incidents as debts swell
OL,6,FChief executive Chris Weston said the
OL,7,Fcompany has made "solid progress" on
OL,8,Fits attempted turnaround, but that
OL,9,Fafter "record rainfall and groundwater
OL,10,Flevels in our region, pollutions and
OL,11,Fspills are unfortunately up".
OL,13,FHe added that the company has reached
OL,14,F"key milestones in establishing a more
OL,15,Fstable financial platform, agreeing a
OL,16,Fliquidity extension transaction
OL,17,Fproposal and progressing our equity
OL,18,Fraise process".
