OL,6,F"The next critical step is receiving
OL,7,Fan investable final determination
OL,8,F(from regulator Ofwat) which is
OL,9,Ffundamental to our future," he added.
OL,11,FThames Water has been at the centre of
OL,12,Fgrowing public outrage over the extent
OL,13,Fof pollution, rising bills, high
OL,14,Fdividends, and executive pay and
OL,15,Fbonuses at the UK's privatised water
OL,16,Ffirms.
OL,18,FIt recently asked regulator Ofwat to
OL,19,Flet it raise average bills by 59% over
OL,20,Fthe next five years, compared with
OL,21,Fcurrent levels.
