OL,3,CThames Water reports 40% rise in
OL,4,Cpollution incidents as debts swell
OL,6,FThe company, which serves about 16
OL,7,Fmillion people, is in the grip of a
OL,8,Ffunding crisis, and needs at least
OL,9,F#3.3 billion in equity over the next
OL,10,Ffive years to keep operating.
OL,12,FThames Water is also the subject of
OL,13,Fbids by several investment groups who
OL,14,Fare looking to buy the company out.
OL,16,FBut the process for an equity
OL,17,Finjection cannot be finalised until
OL,18,FOfwat makes a final decision on
OL,19,Fplanned bill increases, due on
OL,20,FDecember 19.
